# Chat Functionality

The application includes chat functionality for Microsoft Teams integration.

## Key Components

- **Chat Window**: [ms-teams-app/src/components/ChatWindow.tsx](mdc:ms-teams-app/src/components/ChatWindow.tsx) - Main chat interface component
- **Chat List**: [ms-teams-app/src/components/ChatList.tsx](mdc:ms-teams-app/src/components/ChatList.tsx) - Component for displaying chat conversations

These components connect to Microsoft Graph API to fetch and send messages through Microsoft Teams channels.
